<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left is-style-asterisk has-body-font-family has-medium-font-size\" style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:600\">Café Dominicano</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Disfruta de un rico café con todo el sabor que nos caracteriza en la República Dominicana.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":28,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/cafepec/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cafe_granos.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-28\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|10\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"600\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-asterisk\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\",\"fontFamily\":\"body\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left is-style-asterisk has-body-font-family has-medium-font-size\" style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:600\">Cappuccino</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Una experiencia emocionante no tiene por qué sacarte de tu casa.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":29,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/cafepec/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cappuccino.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-29\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|10\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"600\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-asterisk\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\",\"fontFamily\":\"body\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left is-style-asterisk has-body-font-family has-medium-font-size\" style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:600\">Café frío</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Para estos días calurosos, nada más refrescante que un café frío, que te refresca y te energiza.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":30,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/cafepec/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cafe_frio.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-30\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"var:preset|spacing|20\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20)\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\"><!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|10\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"600\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-asterisk\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\",\"fontFamily\":\"body\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left is-style-asterisk has-body-font-family has-medium-font-size\" style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:600\">Café Espresso</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">En los momentos en los que dormirnos no es una opción, un espresso te mantiene despierto.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":31,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-fu